            "value": "<p>This elegant silver band often resembles curling fig leaves and fits around your brow. You gain a +2 item bonus to Deception and Diplomacy checks. When you invest the circlet, you either increase your Charisma score by 2 or increase it to 18, whichever would give you a higher score.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast a 4th-level @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Charm]{Charm} spell (DC 38).</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+2 item bonus to Diplomacy checks</li>\n<li>+2 item bonus to Deception checks</li>\n</ul>"
